701092f-a.title: Bronx: Fowler Avenue - Van Nest Avenue
701092f-a.text:
Fowler Ave., adjoining the S.E. corner of Van Nest Ave., showing
the factory building of the Frank De Rosa Company, auto body builders,
occupying that site. The view is eastward across Bronxdale Ave. (fore-
ground).
July 28, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
